# Model

Ax41 NVME: https://www.hetzner.com/dedicated-rootserver/ax41-nvme/

# Distro

Ubuntu 22.04.2 LTS (Jammy Jellyfish)

# IP

65.108.195.167

# Non Default Configuration

- set hostname to `krondor-ax41-nvme`
- Extend SWAP size from 32 GiB to 64 GiB

# Usable Storage

- 476.96 GiB NVME SSD RAID 1 across 2 512 GiB disks